# Dev-only tooling must NOT be deployed. A root-level Node server file that
# calls .listen() gets auto-detected by Vercel and wrapped as a catch-all
# serverless function, which then serves the ENTIRE site through slow, uncached
# function invocations instead of the static CDN (2s+ per image, blog hangs).
# The dev server now lives in scripts/ (out of root) AND is excluded here so
# the deployment stays a pure static site. Local dev: `node scripts/dev-server.mjs`.
scripts/
server.mjs
